==Translating GZDoom or Raze into your language==
[[File:Gzdoom hexen fr.png|thumb|[[Classes:Korax|Korax]] taunting you in French.]]
It is worth noting that anyone can contribute to GZDoom's localization project, and fluent speakers who wish to contribute to both complete and incomplete languages are welcome. The following spreadsheet contains all localized text data in GZDoom, as well as in Raze, along with all respective translations (both complete and works in progress):
#[https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1pvwXEgytkor9SClCiDn4j5AH7FedyXS-ocCbsuQIXDU/edit?usp=sharing GZDoom & Raze strings]

You can also help by contributing graphics for the missing glyphs in the various fonts. It is possible that your language will require additional characters to be drawn.
*[https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvRvEcBOtXuJ5lBBThAF-rLjGFHhXiSN1x8wfBpW3rk/edit?usp=sharing Character support overview]

More details can be found in {{forum|t=63737|this forum topic}}, which describes in detail how to contribute to the translation of a new language, or improving an existing one.

